botjam
======

fail2ban subset for OpenBSD.

inspired by http://www.vincentdelft.be/post/post_20161106 and
tooling stolen from https://framagit.org/prx/vilain

written from scratch in python.


usage
-----

in pf.conf, add according to your configuration:

	table <botjam> persist
	block quick from <botjam> 

you can easily change the table name in the python script.

thanks
------

